1) Download reads from "http://gage.cbcb.umd.edu/data/Bombus_impatiens/" to work directory ($rootDir).
2) Decompress read files. Make sure the read files are under directory of "$rootDir/Data/original/".
3) Edit "removeAdaptor.sh" to set the variable for "nucmer".
4) In work directory ($rootDir), type "sh removeAdaptor.sh >removeAdaptor.log" and enter to remove adaptor sequence.
5) In work directory ($rootDir), type "sh SOAPdenovo1_pipeline.sh >SOAPdenovo1.log" and enter to assemble reads using SOAPdenovo1.
6) In work directory ($rootDir), type "sh SOAPdenovo2_pipeline.sh >SOAPdenovo2.log" and enter to assemble reads using SOAPdenovo2.
